      <description>&lt;pre class = &#34;poem&#34;&gt;&#xA;Oh Sailor see&#xA;ruins abound&#xA;this house that I&#39;ve built &#xA;on shaky ground.&#xA;&#xA;My fragile place,&#xA;delicate brace,&#xA;already looms the looters&#39; call.&#xA;Any day now I shall fall.&#xA;&#xA;Sailor come,&#xA;before I fall far away.&#xA;Hear my psalm,&#xA;bring hope to this stray.&#xA;Sailor, take me Your way.&#xA;&#xA;Oh Sailor see&#xA;this boat now leaks.&#xA;And in the east &#xA;a great storm peeks.&#xA;&#xA;No old skill &#xA;can save its keel&#xA;from sailing on to the brink. &#xA;Water rises with every blink.&#xA;&#xA;Sailor come, &#xA;before I drift far away,&#xA;hear my psalm&#xA;bring hope to this stray.&#xA;Sailor, take me Your way.&#xA;&lt;/pre&gt;&#xA;&lt;!-- Oh Sailor see &lt;br&gt;&#xA;ruins abound &lt;br&gt;&#xA;this house that I&#39;ve built on shaky ground. &lt;br&gt;&#xA;&#xA;My fragile place, &lt;br&gt;&#xA;delicate brace, &lt;br&gt;&#xA;already looms the looters&#39; call. &lt;br&gt;&#xA;Any day now I shall fall.&#xA;&#xA;Sailor come, &lt;br&gt;&#xA;before I fall far away. &lt;br&gt;&#xA;Hear my psalm, &lt;br&gt;&#xA;bring hope to this stray. &lt;br&gt;&#xA;Sailor, take me Your way. &#xA;&#xA;Oh Sailor see &lt;br&gt;&#xA;this boat now leaks. &lt;br&gt;&#xA;And in the east a great storm peeks. &#xA;&#xA;No old skill &lt;br&gt;&#xA;can save its keel &lt;br&gt;&#xA;from sailing on to the brink. &lt;br&gt;&#xA;Water rises with every blink.&#xA;&#xA;Sailor come, &lt;br&gt;&#xA;before I drift far away, &lt;br&gt;&#xA;hear my psalm &lt;br&gt;&#xA;bring hope to this stray. &lt;br&gt;&#xA;Sailor, take me Your way.&#xA;&#xA;Jesus, take me Your way. --&gt;</description>
